# Agent 1 -- Macro & Market Intelligence System: Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete hybrid LLM+ML intelligence agent that analyzes multi-asset financial markets and produces structured JSON for downstream AI agents.

### Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Binance API<br/>(Crypto)"] --> D["Market Data Aggregator"]
    B["TwelveData API<br/>(Equities, ETFs, Forex)"] --> D
    C["FRED API<br/>(Macro)"] --> M["Macro Data Fetcher"]
    D --> FE["Feature Engine"]
    FE --> RD["Regime Detector<br/>(HMM + RF Ensemble)"]
    FE --> VC["Volatility Classifier"]
    FE --> SR["Risk Detector"]
    M --> MA["Macro Analyzer"]
    MA --> SR
    RD --> CB["LLM Context Builder<br/>(3-Stage Gemini Reasoning)"]
    VC --> CB
    MA --> CB
    SR --> CB
    CB --> OUT["Agent 1 JSON Output"]
    OUT --> V["Pydantic Schema Validation"]
```

### Files Created (20 files)

| Layer | File | Purpose |
|-------|------|---------|
| Config | [settings.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/config/settings.py) | API keys, LLM params, market universes, ML hyperparams |
| Data | [market_data.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/data/market_data.py) | Binance + TwelveData fetchers with TTL cache |
| Data | [macro_data.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/data/macro_data.py) | FRED API for 6 macro dimensions |
| ML | [feature_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/feature_engine.py) | Returns, volatility, momentum, correlation, drawdown |
| ML | [regime_detector.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/regime_detector.py) | HMM + Random Forest ensemble regime detection |
| ML | [volatility_classifier.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/volatility_classifier.py) | Multi-dimensional vol state classification |
| ML | [macro_analyzer.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/macro_analyzer.py) | Macro regime scoring and classification |
| ML | [risk_detector.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/ml/risk_detector.py) | 5-signal systemic risk detection |
| LLM | [gemini_client.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/llm/gemini_client.py) | Provider-agnostic LLM abstraction + factory |
| LLM | [prompts.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/llm/prompts.py) | 3-stage prompt templates |
| LLM | [context_builder.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/llm/context_builder.py) | Multi-stage LLM reasoning pipeline |
| Schema | [agent1_output.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/schemas/agent1_output.py) | Pydantic output contract |
| Agent | [agent1_macro.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/agents/agent1_macro.py) | 10-step orchestrator with graceful degradation |
| Entry | [main.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/main.py) | CLI with mock mode and validation |
| Tests | [test_agent1.py](file:///c:/Users/yassi/OneDrive/Desktop/pfa%20f/tests/test_agent1.py) | 25 tests across all components |

